"%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22content%20theme%20theme_font%22%3E%0A%20%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22title%22%3EBookshelves%20Method%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%20%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22subtitle%22%3EAn%20approach%20to%20memorize%20the%20Quran%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%20%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22author%22%3EIfan%20Dhani%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%20%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22date%22%3EMar%201%2C%202019%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%20%20%3Cp%3EBismillah.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%0A%20%20%3Cp%3EBeing%20an%20Hafidzh%20of%20Quran%20is%20the%20dream%20of%20every%20believer.%20Muslims%20are%20promised%20the%20highest%20degree%20of%20Heaven%20for%20those%20who%20memorize%20the%20Qur'an.%20Therefore%2C%20several%20methods%20of%20memorizing%20the%20Qur'an%20try%20to%20be%20done%2C%20such%20as%20memorizing%20methods%20using%20colors%2C%20memorizing%20by%20optimizing%20the%20senses%20of%20sight%2C%20hearing%2C%20movement%2C%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%0A%20%20%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20article%2C%20I%20will%20share%20how%20to%20memorize%20Quran%20using%20library%20method.%20I%20have%20never%20heard%20of%20a%20method%20similar%20to%20this%20before%2C%20but%20this%20is%20only%20the%20result%20of%20the%20form%20of%20memorizing%20the%20Qur'an%20that%20I%20want.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%0A%20%20%3Cp%3EThis%20method%20uses%20the%20concept%20of%20a%20library%20consisting%20of%20a%20number%20of%20bookshelves%20arranged%20in%20a%20row.%20In%20this%20method%2C%20space%20(space%20for%20storing%20books)%20from%20the%20shelf%20is%20arranged%20into%2010%20rows%20and%205%20columns%20(10x5).%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%0A%20%20%3Cdiv%20style%3D%22width%3A%20100%25%3B%20text-align%3A%20center%3B%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Cimg%20class%3D%22std%22%20src%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontlite.lanterlite.com%2Fassets%2Fcorelite%2Fimg%2Fpage_article%2Farticle%2Flibrarymethod.webp%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%20%20%3Cdiv%20style%3D%22width%3A%20100%25%3B%20text-align%3A%20center%3B%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22img_title%22%3EPic.%20Bookshelves%20Method%20for%20Quran%20Memorizing.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%0A%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3EEach%20space%20stores%20the%20first%20word%20from%20one%20verse%2C%20for%20one%20surah%20in%20the%20Quran.%20Also%20each%20space%20has%20a%20number%20that%20is%20equal%20to%20the%20verse%20number.%20So%20we%20just%20imagine%20this%20bookshelf%20when%20memorizing%20a%20surah%20in%20the%20Qur'an.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%0A%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20benefits%20that%20I%20can%20get%20by%20this%20way%20is%20that%20I%20can%20slowly%20see%20patterns%20from%20a%20number%20of%20verses%20in%20one%20surah%2C%20as%20well%20as%20patterns%20from%20a%20number%20of%20surahs.%20One%20of%20the%20patterns%20I%20meant%20is%20the%20pattern%20of%20the%20relationship%20between%20the%20verse%20number%20(or%20surah)%20and%20the%20meaning%20of%20the%20verse.%20For%20example%2C%20surah%20Ar-Rahman%20(no.%2055)%20and%20Al-Waqi'ah%20(no.%2056)%20together%20discuss%20the%20people%20of%20hell%20starting%20with%20verse%2041%2C%20where%20the%20previous%20verses%20on%20each%20surah%20discuss%20heaven%20or%20about%20the%20greatness%20of%20God.%20Masyaa%20Allah.%20So%20that%20we%20can%20deepen%20our%20knowledge%20regarding%20the%20miracle%20of%20the%20arrangement%20of%20surahs%20and%20verses%20in%20the%20Quran.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%0A%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3EThis%20memorization%20method%20is%20already%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20class%3D%22std%22%20data-tooltip%3D%22Lanter%20Quran%22%20href%3D%22javascript%3A%3B%22%20onclick%3D%22LGen.Page.change_by_url('product%2Flquran')%22%3ELanter%20Quran%3C%2Fa%3E%20Android%20app%20that%20you%20can%20get%20in%20%3Ca%20class%3D%22std%22%20data-tooltip%3D%22Lanter%20Quran%22%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.lanterlite.quranic%22%20target%3D%22_blank%22%3EPlay%20Store%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%20%0A%20%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E"